OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FJeremy Kyle arrives at Winchester
OL,7,FCoroner's Court on Thursday (5
OL,8,FSeptember)
OL,10,FJeremy Kyle has defended his
OL,11,Fpresenting style at an inquest into
OL,12,Fthe death of a man who had been a
OL,13,Fguest on his TV show, saying "it was
OL,14,Fdirect, but it was empathetic, it was
OL,15,Fhonest".
OL,17,FSteve Dymond, 63, from Portsmouth,
OL,18,FHampshire, is believed to have killed
OL,19,Fhimself seven days after filming for
OL,20,Fthe Jeremy Kyle Show in May 2019.
