OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FHe had taken a lie detector test for
OL,7,Fthe programme after being accused of
OL,8,Fcheating on his partner, Jane
OL,9,FCallaghan, from Gosport, Hampshire.
OL,11,FMr Kyle told Winchester Coroner's
OL,12,FCourt that clips from the programme
OL,13,Ffeaturing the case of Mr Dymond and
OL,14,Fhis partner, Jane Callaghan, showed he
OL,15,Fhad "de-escalated... calmed it down".
OL,17,FHe also denied encouraging the
OL,18,Faudience to take against 63-year-old
OL,19,FMr Dymond, telling the inquest: "Not
OL,20,Fat all - I asked them to give them a
OL,21,Fround of applause."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/18
