OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FRachel Spearing, counsel to the
OL,7,Finquest, asked Mr Kyle on Thursday:
OL,8,F"Do you believe he was humiliated?"
OL,10,FThe broadcaster replied: "I do not,
OL,11,Fand I have read over time apparently I
OL,12,Fcalled him a traitor - I didn't - that
OL,13,Fhe was cowering. I did what I always
OL,14,Fdo and always did, it was what the
OL,15,Fshow... as I understood the show is,
OL,16,Fsad as it might sound, it was a
OL,17,Ftypical part."
OL,19,FHe added: "It was a show with my name
OL,20,Fon it, with a production team and an
OL,21,Fafter-care team behind it."
