OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FDefending his presenting style, Mr
OL,7,FKyle said: "I think that people who
OL,8,Fcame on the show... I think the show
OL,9,Fhad been on air for 15 years, and I
OL,10,Fbelieve the approach for conflict
OL,11,Fresolution was always the same. "Yes,
OL,12,Fit was direct, but it was empathetic,
OL,13,Fit was honest."
OL,15,FReferring to Mr Dymond's case, Mr Kyle
OL,16,Fadded: "I de-escalated, I calmed it
OL,17,Fdown and I put them backstage. "That's
OL,18,Fwhat I always believed the show was
OL,19,Fabout - conflict resolution."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/18
