OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FMaya Sikand KC, representing Mr
OL,7,FDymond's family, asked Mr Kyle if he
OL,8,Fhad been "belittling" over his
OL,9,Fhandling of the guest during the
OL,10,Frecording.
OL,12,FShe said he responds: "I can't
OL,13,Fremember when" with Mr Kyle
OL,14,Fcontinuing: "You are lying again
OL,15,Faren't you? You can't remember when
OL,16,Fshe did."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/18
