OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FMs Sikand said Mr Dymond then says: "I
OL,7,Fcross my heart," then Mr Kyle says:
OL,8,F"Just give me the results." She asked
OL,9,FMr Kyle: "This is pretty belittling
OL,10,Fisn't it?
OL,12,FHe replied: "I wouldn't agree with
OL,13,Fyou, I would say it's the part, from
OL,14,Fthe beginning I had a joke with him,
OL,15,Fhe did get upset but he wasn't upset
OL,16,Ffrom the beginning, that's the journey
OL,17,Fand that's the way the Jeremy Kyle
OL,18,Fshow was."
