OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FMr Kyle told the court he was "not
OL,7,Finvolved in the selection of guests"
OL,8,Ffor the show.
OL,10,FHe said: "I want to make a point: I
OL,11,Fhave, in my 14-and-a-half years, not
OL,12,Fbeen involved in the selection of
OL,13,Fguests. I was employed absolutely as
OL,14,Fthe presenter."
OL,16,FHe said he was sent a dossier the
OL,17,Fnight before filming which detailed
OL,18,Fthe approximately 20 guests involved
OL,19,Fin a day's recording.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/18
