OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,F"I had no involvement in the process
OL,7,Fof selection or anything like that,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,FHe later added: "The production, the
OL,11,Fproducing, the after-care, the lie
OL,12,Fdetector test were not my
OL,13,Fresponsibility, I was the presenter."
OL,15,FThe presenter said he had created a
OL,16,Fpersona for the show but had not been
OL,17,Ftrained in handling emotional guests.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/18
