OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FHe said: "The show developed, it was a
OL,7,Fcharacter, a part, by understanding
OL,8,Fthat, from day one, as I keep saying,
OL,9,Fit's conflict resolution so it
OL,10,Finvolved many aspects of many stories
OL,11,Fand many different approaches."
OL,13,FThe court was shown video clips of Mr
OL,14,FDymond being advised about the
OL,15,Fprocesses of the lie detector test
OL,17,FChris Wissun, director of content
OL,18,Fcompliance at ITV at the time,
OL,19,Freturned to the witness box on Thursday
