OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FHe had previously told the hearing
OL,7,Fthat Mr Dymond had been rejected on
OL,8,Fhis first application to the show
OL,9,Fbecause he had disclosed that he had
OL,10,Fbeen diagnosed with depression and
OL,11,Fprescribed anti-depressants.
OL,13,FVideo clips shown in court show Mr
OL,14,FDymond asking the polygraph examiner,
OL,15,Fwho was contracted by ITV to carry out
OL,16,Fthe procedure, whether the test is
OL,17,F"99.9% accurate", to which the
OL,18,Fexaminer replies "They are 95%
OL,19,Faccurate" with a "narrow risk of
OL,20,Ferror".
