OL,6,FMr Wissun previously said a producer
OL,7,Fhad created a draft headline for Mr
OL,8,FDymond's first application on April 9
OL,9,Fwhich read "Missing Viagra and lies
OL,10,Fabout being in the Navy, are you a
OL,11,Fcheat?"
OL,13,FHe said the subsequent letter from Mr
OL,14,FDymond's GP, requesting to support a
OL,15,Fsecond application, was a "very
OL,16,Funusual circumstance".
OL,18,FHe added that Mr Dymond had been given
OL,19,Fa one-to-one assessment despite the
OL,20,Freceipt of the GP's letter.
